1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:12,400
Welcome to the three-minute guided meditation training by all here.

2
00:00:12,400 --> 00:00:35,600
We will now begin five rounds consisting of three minutes each with one minute pause in between.

3
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:53,520
We shall begin the first round in ten seconds.

4
00:00:53,520 --> 00:01:11,440
Round one. Visualize the cosmic sky.

5
00:01:23,520 --> 00:01:41,440
Look at the night sky. See the stars.

6
00:01:41,440 --> 00:02:01,360
See the cosmic sky.

7
00:02:01,360 --> 00:02:25,280
Allow the stars to move closer to you and look at the dark space between the stars.

8
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:33,200
Look at the darkness.

9
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:49,200
Allow the stars to shift away as you move towards darkness.

10
00:02:49,200 --> 00:02:59,120
Look at the darkness.

11
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:19,040
See the dark space.

12
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:36,960
Look at the darkness, approaching your face.

13
00:03:36,960 --> 00:04:00,880
Look at the dark.

14
00:04:00,880 --> 00:04:02,880
End of round one.

15
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:58,880
Round two.

16
00:04:58,880 --> 00:05:12,800
Visualize the full moon inside your chest.

17
00:05:13,440 --> 00:05:30,720
Look at the full moon inside you.

18
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:48,640
The moon and the moonlight lighting up your chest.

19
00:05:48,640 --> 00:06:14,560
Lighting up your stomach, your lungs, your shoulders.

20
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:26,480
Coming upward through your throat.

21
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:46,400
Look at the shining moon inside you.

22
00:06:46,400 --> 00:07:04,320
See the full moon.

23
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:24,240
Full moon inside your chest.

24
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:32,160
The moon and the moonlight.

25
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:48,160
Beaming through your chest, lighting up your throat, your head.

26
00:07:49,120 --> 00:08:00,080
See the full moon.

27
00:08:00,080 --> 00:08:06,080
End of round two.

28
00:08:49,120 --> 00:09:01,120
Round three.

29
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:25,040
Round visualize a star in your belly right in the center of gravity.

30
00:09:25,040 --> 00:09:38,960
Look at the shining star, deep in your belly.

31
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:52,880
Rounded by darkness of the belly.

32
00:09:53,840 --> 00:10:12,800
Sense the star and the starlight emanating from your center.

33
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:38,720
Lighting up through your body, the starlight shining vertically up to the center of your head.

34
00:10:42,800 --> 00:11:06,720
Look at the shining star.

35
00:11:07,680 --> 00:11:16,720
Keep looking.

36
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:26,720
The star, the starlight.

37
00:11:46,720 --> 00:12:04,640
End of round three.

38
00:12:46,720 --> 00:13:04,640
Round four.

39
00:13:04,640 --> 00:13:22,560
Look at the star deep in the center of gravity.

40
00:13:22,560 --> 00:13:40,480
Surrounded by darkness of the belly.

41
00:13:53,520 --> 00:14:12,480
The starlight as the star fades away.

42
00:14:12,480 --> 00:14:38,400
Look at the darkness surrounding the center of gravity.

43
00:14:39,360 --> 00:15:02,320
At the darkness of the belly.

44
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:22,240
Deep in the belly.

45
00:15:32,320 --> 00:16:00,240
Continue to look at the dark in the belly.

46
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:03,680
End of round four.

47
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:52,160
End of round four.

48
00:16:52,480 --> 00:17:00,480
Round five.

49
00:17:00,480 --> 00:17:18,400
Now visualize the cosmic sky in front of you.

50
00:17:30,480 --> 00:17:48,400
Move closer to the stars.

51
00:18:01,200 --> 00:18:20,400
You move beyond the stars towards the darkness.

52
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:38,320
See the deep dark beyond all planets, galaxies.

53
00:18:50,400 --> 00:19:08,320
The darkness approaching to your face.

54
00:19:20,400 --> 00:19:46,320
Touch the darkness.

55
00:19:46,800 --> 00:19:58,240
Stay in the dark.

56
00:20:00,800 --> 00:20:06,240
End of round five.

57
00:20:47,280 --> 00:21:00,240
Round six.

58
00:21:00,240 --> 00:21:14,160
Visualize a single star in the dark sky.

59
00:21:30,240 --> 00:21:38,160
Any direction.

60
00:21:39,040 --> 00:21:48,160
See how the star is moving closer to you.

61
00:21:48,160 --> 00:22:06,080
Inside and forming into an image of sun in front of you.

62
00:22:06,720 --> 00:22:24,000
And the sun light shining onto your face, onto your body, shining through.

63
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:33,920
The sun is moving closer.

64
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:41,920
The giant sun in front of you.

65
00:22:41,920 --> 00:22:55,840
The light peers through your body as you enter the space of sun.

66
00:22:55,840 --> 00:23:19,760
Enter the sun light lighting on the entire space.

67
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:31,680
You absorb into the sun.

68
00:23:31,680 --> 00:23:43,600
You become the sunlight.

69
00:24:01,680 --> 00:24:07,120
End of round six.

70
00:24:31,680 --> 00:24:37,120
End of round six.

